---
// ServerlessVsContainers.astro — Side-by-side comparison
---
<div class="svc-wrap">
  <h3 class="svc-title">Serverless vs Containers — Head to Head</h3>
  <div class="svc-grid">
    <div class="svc-col svc-col--sl">
      <span class="svc-hl svc-hl--cyan">Serverless (Lambda/Cloud Functions)</span>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Scaling</span><span class="svc-val">Automatic, per-request</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Cold start</span><span class="svc-val svc-val--bad">100ms – 5s (depends on runtime)</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Pricing</span><span class="svc-val">Per invocation + duration</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Max runtime</span><span class="svc-val">15 min (Lambda limit)</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">State</span><span class="svc-val">Stateless only</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Ops burden</span><span class="svc-val svc-val--good">Near zero</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Debugging</span><span class="svc-val svc-val--bad">Hard — distributed + ephemeral</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-col svc-col--ct">
      <span class="svc-hl svc-hl--purple">Containers (ECS/K8s/Cloud Run)</span>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Scaling</span><span class="svc-val">HPA/KEDA, configure yourself</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Cold start</span><span class="svc-val svc-val--good">None (always running) or ~2s (scale from 0)</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Pricing</span><span class="svc-val">Per-hour compute (always on)</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Max runtime</span><span class="svc-val svc-val--good">Unlimited</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">State</span><span class="svc-val">Stateful possible (volumes)</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Ops burden</span><span class="svc-val svc-val--bad">Medium-High (patching, scaling, networking)</span></div>
      <div class="svc-row"><span class="svc-lbl">Debugging</span><span class="svc-val svc-val--good">SSH in, check logs, traditional</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<style>
  .svc-wrap{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1e293b);border-radius:16px;padding:2rem;margin:2rem 0;border:1px solid #334155}
  .svc-title{color:#f1f5f9;font-size:1.15rem;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 1.5rem}
  .svc-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px}@media(max-width:600px){.svc-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .svc-col{padding:14px;background:rgba(0,0,0,.2);border-radius:12px;border:1px solid #334155}
  .svc-col--sl{border-top:2px solid #06b6d4}.svc-col--ct{border-top:2px solid #818cf8}
  .svc-hl{display:block;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;font-family:monospace;margin-bottom:10px}.svc-hl--cyan{color:#06b6d4}.svc-hl--purple{color:#818cf8}
  .svc-row{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b}.svc-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
  .svc-lbl{color:#64748b;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:600}.svc-val{color:#e2e8f0;font-size:.68rem;text-align:right}
  .svc-val--good{color:#4ade80}.svc-val--bad{color:#f59e0b}
</style>
